text:
I just opened a role for an events manager on my team: <https://angel.co/company/fishtown-analytics/jobs/688926-events-manager>

The company is called Fishtown Analytics, but this role is producing events for dbt (data build tool) -- our open source product and the growing community around it. There are ~1100 companies using dbt today and over 3000 people in our Slack community.

We're a small team (<20 people) based in Philadelphia, but are open to hiring anyone in the continental US. We have several remote employees and I managed a remote team at HubSpot so this is a not a "we'll make you suffer for the luxury of being remote" situation :slightly_smiling_face:

If you know someone, I would love to speak with them! If you have questions, don't hesitate to DM me.

:heart:
